Kusolwa ukuthi ngomhla ka-5 kwephezulu umsebenzi wasesitolo owayevala ntambamba wakhonjwa yisigebengu ngesibhamu samphoqa ukuba avule. Kulesi sigameko kwathathwa imali nezinye izinto ezazisesitolo. Umsolwa kuthiwa wabaleka ngezinyawo esuka esitolo, amaphoyisa akholwa ukuthi owesilisa osesithombeni angawasiza ngolwazi olungaholela ekutheni aphenye ngempumelelo icala lokubamba inkunzi kuhlonyiwe. Ongaba nolwazi uyacelwa ukuthi athinte uSgt Sankar ku-036 637 9517 noma ashayele inombolo yeCrime Stop ethi 08600 101111.